data.description: Welcome to this recently renovated home in the Hunters Reserve neighborhood.  This bi-level home features 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, with a garden level basement and a 2 car garage with an extended driveway that can fit a boat or RV. New roof installed in 2019 and HVAC installed in 2020. The kitchen has new cabinets, new countertops, new stainless steel appliances featuring an open concept and a finished basement.  Beautifully updated with new flooring throughout. The backyard features a large fenced yard and a deck.
